<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>306</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tumlam phaicham apat,
 Hetsakna la a hung;
 Ginumna, ginumna, ginumna, Krista di'n,
 A la gi thang zel chuh;
 Muol tinin a sak pih,
 Zie ginumna, Krista dinga ginumna thu chuh.

[V2]
 &quot;Zo zel din kuon un!&quot; (2)
 I lamkai pauin A tii;
 A thupiek awi hitiu,
 Gam la pai zieng hitiu;
 Krista din I ginum nau, I ginum nau ziekin!

[V3]
 2. Mi hangsan te'n ngai un,
 Sietlei kimvela thang;
 Ginumna, ginumna, ginumna Krista din!
 Tho un pang ngam dingin;
 Hilhna thudik phuong un,
 Zie ginumna, Krista dinga ginumna thu chuh!

[V4]
 3. Lawi muon um hun zawm un,
 Setan gal nuoisieh din;
 Krista dinga ginumna, ginumna ziekin!
 Setan puonlap zak na'h;
 Gospel phuong zak hitiu,
 Zie ginumna, Krista dinga ginumna thu hi!

[V5]
 4. Khanglai' hatna I ngau,
 Tu'n Isu kengbul ah;
 Krista dinga ginumna, ginumna ziekin!
 Gospel phuongzak hitiu,
 Khawvel gam tin chengah;
 Zie ginumna, Krista dinga ginumna thu chuh.</lyrics>
<title>LOYALTY TO CHRIST</title>
</song>